{"tid":2504990,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"繼阿里巴巴之後 市場監管總局對美團涉嫌壟斷行為立案調查","createTime":"2021-04-26T09:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T09:50:12.000Z","uid":99885,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e67121f756d81115d0d814afd56446eaa1de6bbb","tid":2504990,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:33:52.000Z","msg":"國家市場監督管理總局公布，近日根據舉報，依法對美團實施「二選一」等涉嫌壟斷行為立案調查。<br />\n<br />\n內媒報道，美團微信公眾號發文稱，今日(26日)集團接到國家市場監管總局通知，依法對美團涉嫌壟斷行為立案調查。公司將積極配合監管部門調查，進一步提升業務合規管理水平，保障用戶以及各方主體合法權益，促進行業長期健康發展，切實履行社會責任。"},{"pid":"91220defa6347b02bb66e975e8c67931f8c41c97","tid":2504990,"uid":55335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:36:22.000Z","msg":"嚟料"},{"pid":"2502157ad830f1e9358e154ed866c5f71ad77a31","tid":2504990,"uid":266391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:42:22.000Z","msg":"回血劍"},{"pid":"cc8324d2188032c70df38d19f863e4d54d0ae7f1","tid":2504990,"uid":204245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:42:54.000Z","msg":"麵神今日一出po.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5728511fcafef72debeb8d795c90d755f4504f62","tid":2504990,"uid":151531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:44:00.000Z","msg":"麵神旗下ATM<br />\n幾時到T"},{"pid":"aecbffaae8227b67ddf1011dff6ea974627a4388","tid":2504990,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:47:16.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec65ba99a92e79a81b7d3111adf0b57f25ff432","tid":2504990,"uid":109721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:47:54.000Z","msg":"drop to zero<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7ca9a5974d0b7420b91c4aabb7ee7cc10c4f1d","tid":2504990,"uid":